prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon sloth wearing a festive party hat, hanging upside-down from a tree branch that sags slightly under its weight. The sloth is smiling dreamily, eyes half-closed, clutching a single, brightly colored balloon by its string. Below the sloth, a lone, slightly squashed cupcake with a single lit candle sits on the ground, as if it just dropped. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, whimsical watercolor style with visible paper texture. Artistic splotches and organic paint bleeds add to the handcrafted feel. Centered below the sloth is the text "happy birthday" in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script.
